Constructor:
-help us give initial values to the fields of a class

Why use a constructor?:
-help us write cleaner code
-give us more ctrl over values that an end user can assign to the fields of a class

Syntax of Constructor:
Access modifier className (parameters){

}
Class Dog{
String name;
public Dog(String dogName) //<- needs to be same as class name
name= dogName;
}